description: Seattle Transit provides step-by-step transit directions for getting from one neighborhood to another in Seattle. The handy card in the Alexa app helps one take the directions with them while on the go. More features to come.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Seattle Transit for directions from Ballard to Capitol Hill
Alexa, ask Seattle Transit for directions from Ballard
name: Seattle Transit
shortDescription: Get step-by-step transit directions between neighborhoods in Seattle.
